history.content:
You will have quick 15-minute one-to-one conservations with experienced upperclassmen to discuss internships (contacting, resume, interview), research (emailing, writing project proposals, application process), classes (course selection, professor/class-specific advice), and more! This is an open space to take advantage of the knowledge our mentors have accumulated during their years and experiences here! 

Facebook Link: https://www.facebook.com/events/200043101378857

Sign up to be a MENTEE: https://tinyurl.com/u7ccvb7
history.subject: Come to IEEE Speed Mentoring this Thursday(March 5th) from 6-8pm in Cory 293!
